[LOG](../../../logs/2012/2012-08-09-log.txt).


## President's Report

Bdale reported that an SPI BoF had taken place at DebConf 12 in July. A
[video](http://meetings-archive.debian.net/pub/debian-meetings/2012/debconf12/low/847_SPI_BOF.ogv)
is available. He also informed us that he was taking [early retirement](http://www.gag.com/bdale/blog/posts/Early_Retirement.html)
from HP at the end of August.


